    "en": {
      "title": "Susil, the new leader of the Parliament?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that Minister Susil Premajayantha is going to be appointed as the new Leader of the Parliament.",
        "It is also known that the decision will be announced in Parliament today.",
        "Mr. Dinesh Gunawardena was the leader of the Parliament before this. With his appointment as the Prime Minister, the post of House Leader became vacant."
      ],
